    <item>
      <title>哈里斯准备结束演讲，重点关注 1 月 6 日的经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/harris-dc-speech-to-contrast-with-trump-focus-on-jan-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯将于周二晚上在华盛顿历史悠久的国家广场发表最后陈词，她希望将前总统唐纳德·特朗普描绘成一个充满怨恨和报复的人，并希望美国人愿意翻开新的一页。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/harris-dc-speech-to-contrast-with-trump-focus-on-jan-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>真主党任命被暗杀领导人纳斯鲁拉的继任者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/hezbollah-names-replacement-for-assassinated-leader-nasrallah</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黎巴嫩激进组织真主党宣布，纳伊姆·卡西姆将成为其新领导人，接替一个多月前被以色列暗杀的哈桑·纳斯鲁拉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/hezbollah-names-replacement-for-assassinated-leader-nasrallah</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 08:42:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克警方在冲突后对反对派领导人展开立案调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/mozambique-police-opens-case-against-opposition-head-after-clash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克执法官员已对反对党领导人维南西奥·蒙德拉纳 (Venâncio Mondlane) 提起刑事诉讼，此前，反对党支持者在 10 月 9 日选举中因涉嫌舞弊而引发的暴力抗议活动中焚烧了一座警察局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/mozambique-police-opens-case-against-opposition-head-after-clash</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 07:47:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利古里亚州长竞选中候选人获胜，梅洛尼获得提振</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/meloni-gets-boost-from-candidate-s-win-in-liguria-governor-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔治亚·梅洛尼 (Giorgia Meloni) 提名的利古里亚大区州长候选人以微弱优势赢得选举，增强了意大利总理政府抵御持续动荡的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/meloni-gets-boost-from-candidate-s-win-in-liguria-governor-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 05:01:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>首尔警告驻俄朝鲜军队正向前线进发</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/north-korea-s-top-envoy-visits-russia-as-troops-approach-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国警告称，派往俄罗斯协助莫斯科对乌克兰战争的朝鲜军队和将军可能正在转向前线，这一迹象表明冲突即将蔓延并卷入新的参与者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/north-korea-s-top-envoy-visits-russia-as-troops-approach-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 01:37:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世界正准备迎接特朗普回归之际，日本面临转向内向的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/japan-risks-turning-inward-just-as-world-braces-for-trump-return</link>
      <description><![CDATA[正当全世界为唐纳德·特朗普可能重返白宫做准备并期待其给美国关键盟友带来压力之时，日本却有可能进入新一轮政策停滞阶段。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/japan-risks-turning-inward-just-as-world-braces-for-trump-return</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 01:30:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国投资者从抗议数据中寻找下一步刺激措施的线索</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/xi-stimulus-clues-found-in-protest-data-showing-economic-stress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多年来，记录中国的抗议活动一直是政治活动家的任务。现在，它引起了投资者的注意，他们试图预测北京是否会转向火箭筒式刺激政策]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/xi-stimulus-clues-found-in-protest-data-showing-economic-stress</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 22:00:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登最终决定限制美国对中国芯片和人工智能技术的投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/biden-finalizes-curbs-on-us-investment-in-chinese-chip-ai-tech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府最终确定对美国个人和企业对中国半导体、量子计算和人工智能等先进技术的投资进行限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/biden-finalizes-curbs-on-us-investment-in-chinese-chip-ai-tech</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际清算银行辩论终止普京考虑的削弱美元的项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/bis-debates-ending-project-eyed-by-putin-to-undermine-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京将该基础技术视为规避制裁的工具并可能破坏美元在全球金融体系中的主导地位后，国际清算银行正在讨论是否关闭试点跨境支付平台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/bis-debates-ending-project-eyed-by-putin-to-undermine-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 18:34:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡塔尔重启谈判 以色列愿意在加沙短暂停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/israel-hamas-war-netanyahu-open-to-short-truce-in-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡表示，他愿意在以色列与哈马斯的战争中实现短暂停火，以便释放目前仍被伊朗支持的加沙激进组织扣押的约 100 名人质中的少数人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/israel-hamas-war-netanyahu-open-to-short-truce-in-gaza</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 16:22:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
